"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"With each passing year, the crypto universe continues to expand into different business areas: new currencies, financial tools, investing opportunities, games, NFTs, etc. When it comes to selecting a platform, you would probably choose what suits you most. But what if you need a wide set of services as well as the proper level of security?\\n\\nWelcome to the world of all-in-one crypto platforms, where the future of the blockchain industry lies. Most of them allow customers to buy and sell cryptocurrencies easily and securely store their assets.Â \\n\\nAn all-in-one crypto platform usually combines relevant services for both newbies and professionals. Such platforms aim to provide an ideal set of essential tools needed to successfully operate in the industry.\\n\\nTo provide users with the best trading experience, **cryptocurrency platform Phemex** has established high standards and stands out from the crowd. Phemex's priority is to empower everyone to trade simply and manage risk efficiently. The all-in-one platform enables access to the right set of tools for efficient cryptocurrency trading and **money management**.\\n\\n\\\"We place customers first. All of our features and tools are designed with this philosophy in mind. This is why our development team is directly available and constantly gathering feedback, comments, and requests from our community on social media,\\\" says a statement on its official website.\\n\\n \\n \",\"timestamp\":1638367707,\"title\":\"All-in-one Cryptocurrency Platforms Both For Newbies and Professionals\"},\"digest\":\"NPYSNq_qQwbrI8O_cHWGSwOmJlV_raRwU9wNLUUntcQ\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x65a5aBB63bb431a9B8377487d0A8cd2a797856f0\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"h1NxghbffDjz-hVvjN1awMheoJzitsqN1zWH9oFGZ9E\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"2YOsQ4KRH9r4-fWhZBHyak-BYJo3w-VdJnlzLt86M7g\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"T96_9jgKnxxF